body:
* The feeling that I have to re-earn everything that I had really sucks and makes me not want to play anymore 
{{sticker:slayer-jinx-unamused}} 
* The lack of champion shard rerolling makes this grind all the more frustrating.
{{sticker:zombie-nunu-bummed}} 
* Lacking access to uniquely varied gameplay styles and tools provided by certain champions makes team comp and gameplay difficult.
{{sticker:sona-playing}} 
* The lost motivation keeps me from putting in the effort to complete missions.
{{sticker:cass-cry}} 
* This &quot;League Depression&quot; always has my mood while in-game considerably low which affects both performance and overall team outlook.
{{sticker:sg-janna}} 

Having my main account permabanned sucks lol but at the end of the day I do enjoy playing Lisandra and Akali at least?

